title: Youtuber with 37 videos, you might like??
body:
Hey everyone! I make youtube vids of lol for fun, and I got 37 videos at the moment. Maybe you might like some of them so check it out if ya want something to do. If not its great for the music, you get to know a side of me that is my passion. 

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-hearts}} 

Thanks,
SentienceLOL 
OCE

[https://www.youtube.com/c/sentienceLOL](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRkVTm4pwhKZiyguC-JOhhA)
